{
  "title": "spring-boot-maven-plugin 插件的作用",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">OM 文件中添加了“org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-maven-plugin”插件。在添加了该插件之后，当运行“mvn package”进行打包时，会打包成一个可以直接运行的 JAR 文件，使用“java -jar”命令就可以直接运行。这在很大程度上简化了应用的部署，只需要安装了 JRE 就可以运行。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">可以在POM中，指定生成 的是Jar还是War。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&lt;project xmlns=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd\"&gt;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&lt;!-- ... --&gt;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&lt;packaging&gt;jar&lt;/packaging&gt;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&lt;!-- ... --&gt;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&lt;/project&gt;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">你还可以指定要执行的类，如果不指定的话，Spring会找有这个【<code class=\"literal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Monaco, Menlo, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 14.4px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); white-space: nowrap; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 4px;\">public static void main(String[] args)</code>】方法的类，当做可执行的类。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你想指定的话，可以用下面两个方法：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1，如果你的POM是继承<span class=\"comment-copy\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">spring-boot-starter-parent</span>的话，只需要下面的指定就行。</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "json",
      "data": "<properties>\n    <!-- The main class to start by executing java -jar -->\n    <start-class>com.mycorp.starter.HelloWorldApplication</start-class>\n</properties>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<span style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2，如果你的POM不是继承</span><span class=\"comment-copy\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">spring-boot-starter-parent</span><span style=\"color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">的话，需要下面的指定。</span>"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "json",
      "data": "<plugin>\n      <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>\n      <artifactId>spring-boot-maven-plugin</artifactId>\n      <version>1.3.5.RELEASE</version>\n      <configuration>\n        <mainClass>${start-class}</mainClass>\n        <layout>ZIP</layout>\n      </configuration>\n      <executions>\n        <execution>\n          <goals>\n            <goal>repackage</goal>\n          </goals>\n        </execution>\n      </executions>\n</plugin>"
    }
  ]
}